Day 93: Using Ansible Conditionals

Date: December 21, 2025
Overview
Implemented conditional logic in playbooks.
Key Concepts Learned

When statements
Fact-based conditions
Variable-based conditions
Complex conditionals

Playbook
yaml- name: Install package based on OS
  yum:
    name: httpd
    state: present
  when: ansible_os_family == "RedHat"

- name: Install package on Ubuntu
  apt:
    name: apache2
    state: present
  when: ansible_distribution == "Ubuntu"

- name: Conditional deployment
  command: /deploy-script.sh
  when: 
    - environment == "production"
    - ansible_processor_cores >= 4

Challenges Faced
Complex conditional logic and understanding fact variables.
